<div id="tiktok-trend-discovery"></div>
<h2>How to do TikTok trend discovery using TikTok Creative Center and more</h2>
<p>To help businesses and creators know what‚Äôs trending on TikTok, the platform has a few options within the app. Plus, TikTok offers a library full of video ideas, tips, and inspiration called the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok Creative Center</a>. Here are some of the top ways you can do TikTok trend discovery using resources TikTok provides‚Äîincluding TikTok Creative Center:</p>
<h3>1. Check out top creators</h3>
<p>In the Trends section of TikTok Creative Center, you can find videos from top TikTok creators and influencers when you select the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/inspiration/popular/creator/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Creators tab</a>. Not only can this help you find TikTok trends by seeing what patterns top creators are following, but it can also uncover <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/03/23/how-to-become-a-social-media-influencer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">potential influencers</a> for your brand to work with.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-creative-center.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - trend discovery using tiktok creative center" width="900" height="476" class="aligncenter wp-image-78534 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-creative-center.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-creative-center-480x254.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>2. Look at the trending TikTok videos tab</h3>
<p>In the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/inspiration/popular/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Videos tab</a> of TikTok Creative Center Trends, you can see what videos are trending on TikTok regardless of whether it‚Äôs from a highly followed creator or not. This is a great place to source viral videos your business could mimic, <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/03/11/how-to-stitch-on-tiktok" target="_blank" rel="noopener">duet, or stitch</a>.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-tiktok-videos.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - top tiktok videos screenshot" width="900" height="555" class="aligncenter wp-image-78547 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-tiktok-videos.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-tiktok-videos-480x296.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>3. Review popular hashtags</h3>
<p>In the TikTok Creative Center, under Trends, the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/inspiration/popular/hashtag/pc/en?rid=yt88fvgsgm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hashtags tab</a> allows you to track trending <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/04/07/tiktok-hashtags" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok hashtags related to your industry</a>. You could also use the search bar to find hashtags related to keywords your business may be targeting.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-hashtags.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - trending tiktok hashtags" width="900" height="498" class="aligncenter wp-image-78546 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-hashtags.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-hashtags-480x266.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>4. Find popular songs</h3>
<p>The final part of the Trends section of TikTok Creative Center is the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/inspiration/popular/music/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Songs tab</a>. Here, you can discover trending TikTok audio clips and songs to use in your videos. It‚Äôs broken out into two sections.</p>
<p>The popular section can help you find the most frequently used songs within your selected timeframe, and you can filter out for those approved for business use. The breakout section includes both songs and user-generated audio clips that are rising in popularity‚Äîwhich can help you get ahead of TikTok trends.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-breakout.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - songs" width="947" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-78545 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-breakout.jpg 947w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-breakout-480x304.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 947px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>5. Use the TikTok Commercial Music Library</h3>
<p>In addition to the Trends section within Creative Center, you can use the TikTok Commercial Music Library (found in the Creative Tools section) for trend discovery. The <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/music/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Commercial Music Library</a> holds all pre-cleared music for both organic TikTok content and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/tiktok-ads-bidding">TikTok Ads</a>. There are tons of ways you can filter and sort your results to find trending songs that best fit your content.</p>
<p>Alternatively, check out the Playlist tab to find a viral TikTok music playlist. Plus, find tons of other playlists of new songs, songs popular in video games or memes, sounds for businesses, and more.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-viral-playlist.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - viral tiktok song playlist" width="900" height="479" class="aligncenter wp-image-78544 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-viral-playlist.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-viral-playlist-480x255.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>6. Read up on TikTok trend perspectives</h3>
<p>To make TikTok trend discovery even easier, the TikTok Creative Center also includes a Trends section which includes <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/trends/hub/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Trend Perspectives</a>. The purpose of Trends Perspectives is to educate TikTok marketers and advertisers on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/05/23/tiktok-ads-targeting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok audience behaviors</a>. With this resource, you can predict how TikTok trends in your industry may grow and evolve.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-trend-perspectives.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - trend perspectives" width="776" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-78543 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-trend-perspectives.jpg 776w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-trend-perspectives-480x371.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 776px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>7. Research successful TikTok creative strategies</h3>
<p>Discover which TikTok trends have been successful in the past using the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/quicktok/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Creative Strategies</a> page under Creative Center‚Äôs Education tab. This is where you can find <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/08/23/tiktok-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok marketing</a> case studies, creative tips, and quick TikTok tutorials.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-creative-strategies.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - example of tiktok creative strategies" width="900" height="576" class="aligncenter wp-image-78542 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-creative-strategies.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-creative-strategies-480x307.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>8. Use the TikTok Ads library and Top Ads Dashboard</h3>
<p>The <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/09/14/tiktok-ads-library" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok Ads library</a> can be a secret weapon for businesses looking to do TikTok trend discovery since it allows you to research <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/tiktok-ads-bidding">TikTok ads</a> from competitors. If you‚Äôre familiar with the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/06/06/facebook-ad-library" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook ads library</a>, know that the TikTok ads library functions in the same way where it‚Äôs meant to provide transparency for users and help businesses source video inspiration.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-countries.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - available country data example" width="777" height="427" class="aligncenter wp-image-75944 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-countries.jpg 777w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-countries-480x264.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 777px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Currently, the TikTok Ads library only pulls data from ads running in Europe. That said, if you‚Äôre based outside of Europe, you can still use it to get a general understanding of how different types of TikTok Ads are trending for similar businesses in your industry.</p>
<p>Alternatively, you can head to the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/inspiration/topads/pc/en?period=30&amp;region=US" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Top Ads Dashboard</a> within the Inspiration section of the TikTok Creative Center to see the highest-performing ads within your chosen criteria for any region.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-top-tiktok-ads.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - top tiktok ads example" width="854" height="434" class="aligncenter wp-image-78552 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-top-tiktok-ads.jpg 854w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-top-tiktok-ads-480x244.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 854px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>9. Find hot keywords with Keyword Insights</h3>
<p>Also within the Inspiration section of Creative Center is the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/keyword-insights/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Keyword Insights</a> tool. With this resource, you can explore trending <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/tiktok-seo">keywords</a> to ensure your TikTok video scripts and captions are hitting all the right buzzwords for your business to <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/target-market-examples/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">connect with your target market</a>.</p>
<p>This can be key (no pun intended) to your TikTok trend discovery because you can see which keywords have had the biggest jumps in popularity along with related videos that could inspire your own. Just be sure to get an idea of the core terms you want to target using other <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/02/20/cross-platform-keyword-research-tools" target="_blank" rel="noopener">keyword research tools</a> first.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-keyword-insights.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - tiktok keyword insights" width="881" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-78541 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-keyword-insights.jpg 881w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-keyword-insights-480x327.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 881px, 100vw" /></p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f6e0.png" alt="üõ†" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Need a tool to help you prep for using TikTok Keyword Insights? Check out our <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/keywords?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_Keywords_KWTool" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Free Keyword Research Tool</a>.</p>
<h3>10. Discover trending TikTok products</h3>
<p>If competitive analysis is something your business needs to prioritize during your TikTok trend discovery process, the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/top-products/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Top Products</a> section of the Inspiration tab within Creative Center should be your go-to tool. It provides you with information on trending products within a chosen category.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-top-products.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - top tiktok products " width="732" height="513" class="aligncenter wp-image-78530 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-top-products.jpg 732w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-top-products-480x336.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 732px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>From there, you could measure your videos‚Äô performance metrics against averages within your industry and see trending TikTok content for those products.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-products-performance-analytics.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - top products analytics" width="929" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-78540 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-products-performance-analytics.jpg 929w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-products-performance-analytics-480x310.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 929px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>11. Browse your own TikTok FYP</h3>
<p>The best resource for <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/discover/tiktok-trend-discovery-products?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok trend discovery</a>? Your own TikTok FYP! The <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/what-is-fyp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok For You Page (FYP)</a> serves up content related to other accounts and videos you‚Äôve already interacted with. Try to be active on your own TikTok account and get into the mind of your ideal customer. Once you start seeing <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/10/07/how-to-get-on-tiktok-fyp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">relevant content on your TikTok FYP</a>, you can get a feel for which types of TikTok trends are favored most by your audience.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-fyp.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - tiktok fyp" width="358" height="575" class="aligncenter wp-image-78531 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-fyp.jpg 358w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-fyp-187x300.jpg 187w" sizes="(max-width: 358px) 100vw, 358px" /></p>
<h3>12. Use the TikTok trend discovery page</h3>
<p>Finally, since TikTok content is so heavily reliant on what‚Äôs trending, there‚Äôs a dedicated <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/discover/tiktok-trends?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok trend discovery page</a> right from within the platform. Any user can browse through this portion of the app to see videos related to the biggest TikTok trends.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-page.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery page screenshot" width="900" height="391" class="aligncenter wp-image-78539 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-page.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-page-480x209.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<div id="how-to-find-tiktok-trends"></div>
<h2>6 more ways to do TikTok trend discovery (beyond the TikTok Creative Center)</h2>
<p>While the TikTok app and TikTok Creative Center will likely be your primary sources for TikTok trend discovery, you‚Äôll want a well-rounded look at what‚Äôs hot in your industry. Try to keep an open mind and consider other ways TikTok trends rise in popularity using these ideas below.</p>
<h3>1. Look at YouTube Shorts</h3>
<p><a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-make-youtube-shorts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube Shorts</a> are short-form videos on YouTube that are comparable to TikTok videos in length, styling, and format. Because of this, brands typically have some crossover between their <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/11/08/tiktok-vs-youtube" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok and YouTube</a> Shorts content. So, if you scroll through <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/youtube-shorts-ideas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">popular YouTube Shorts</a>, you‚Äôll also likely be able to discover new TikTok trends.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-youtube-shorts.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - youtube shorts home page example" width="601" height="522" class="aligncenter wp-image-78532 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-youtube-shorts.jpg 601w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-youtube-shorts-480x417.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 601px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>2. See what‚Äôs trending on Instagram Reels</h3>
<p>Like YouTube Shorts, <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/what-is-instagram-reels-for-business/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram Reels</a> are another opportunity to find trending short-form videos similar to TikToks. You‚Äôll likely find many of the same concepts trending on both <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/02/16/tiktok-vs-instagram-reels-ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram Reels and TikTok</a>. In fact, it‚Äôs not uncommon for viral TikToks to be reposted to Reels!</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-instagram-reels.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - instagram reels example" width="354" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-78538 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-instagram-reels.jpg 354w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-instagram-reels-177x300.jpg 177w" sizes="(max-width: 354px) 100vw, 354px" /></p>
<h3>3. Refer to your historical performance</h3>
<p>The best way to discover which TikTok trends may or may not work for your business is through trial and error. As you get started on TikTok, find a few TikTok trends to start testing out. As you continue to market and advertise on TikTok over time, benchmark your progress.</p>
<p>Over time, you can look back at your historical performance using your <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/creators/creator-portal/en-us/tiktok-content-strategy/understanding-your-analytics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok analytics</a> and make data-backed conclusions for how new TikTok trends may evolve based on your past videos that were more or less successful.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-data.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - tiktok analytics" width="346" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-78537 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-data.jpg 346w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-data-173x300.jpg 173w" sizes="(max-width: 346px) 100vw, 346px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/creators/creator-portal/en-us/tiktok-content-strategy/understanding-your-analytics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>4. Use your marketing planning calendar</h3>
<p>You can predict what might be trending on TikTok based on upcoming events throughout the year. Use a <a href="https://marketing.localiq.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsite2024MarketingCalendar.html?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Guide_2024MarketingCalendar_Download" target="_blank" rel="noopener">marketing planning calendar</a> like the example below to prep your content according to what‚Äôs relevant to your audience during any given month or season.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-localiq-marketing-calendar.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - example marketing planning calendar from localiq" width="645" height="507" class="aligncenter wp-image-78533 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-localiq-marketing-calendar.jpg 645w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-localiq-marketing-calendar-480x377.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 645px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>5. Try Google video search</h3>
<p>You can discover more TikTok trends using Google video search. Google video search ranks videos based on indicators such as popularity and relevancy to your search query‚Äîmaking it a great option to get TikTok trend ideas from top sources like YouTube, TikTok, and industry websites.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-video-search.jpg" alt="tiktok trend discovery - google video search screenshot" width="900" height="475" class="aligncenter wp-image-78536 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-video-search.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tiktok-trend-discovery-video-search-480x253.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h2>Using TikTok trend discovery to your advantage</h2>
<p>There are tons of ways to do TikTok trend discovery for your business. Taking even just a few minutes to understand TikTok trends can make your content planning a breeze.</p>
<p>However, if you don‚Äôt have time to stay on top of TikTok trends, that‚Äôs okay too! See how <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/marketing-services" target="_blank" rel="noopener">our solutions</a> can help your business capitalize on social media trends on TikTok and beyond.</p>
<p>Here is how to do TikTok trend discovery using the TikTok Creative Center:</p>
<ol>
<li>Check out top creators</li>
<li>Look at the trending TikTok videos tab</li>
<li>Review popular hashtags</li>
<li>Read up on TikTok trend perspectives</li>
<li>Find popular songs</li>
<li>Use the TikTok commercial music library</li>
<li>Research successful TikTok creative strategies</li>
<li>Use the TikTok Ads library</li>
<li>Find hot keywords with keyword insights</li>
<li>Discover trending TikTok products</li>
<li>Browse your own TikTok FYP</li>
<li>Use the TikTok trend discover page</li>
</ol>
<p>More ways to do TikTok trend discovery (beyond the TikTok Creative Center):</p>
<ol>
<li>Look at YouTube Shorts</li>
<li>See what‚Äôs trending on Instagram Reels</li>
<li>Refer to your historical performance</li>
<li>Use your marketing planning calendar</li>
<li>Try Google video search</li>
</ol>
