		<item>
		<title>11 Sneaky Ways to Use the TikTok Ads Library for Better, More Engaging Ads</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/09/14/tiktok-ads-library</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Susie Marino]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 14 Sep 2023 20:16:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[TikTok]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.wordstream.com/?p=75942</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>Learn how the TikTok Ads library tool for your business when you're trying to beat out the competition on TikTok Ads. </p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/09/14/tiktok-ads-library">11 Sneaky Ways to Use the TikTok Ads Library for Better, More Engaging Ads</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>As online ad platforms evolve more privacy-friendly approaches to audience targeting, ad transparency naturally has grown into a need, not a want, for both consumers and advertisers.</p>
<p>Published ads on platforms like Google Ads, Facebook, and TikTok are public knowledge and should be treated as such. Consumers have a right to know about the ad being put in front of them, and advertisers should also be able to accurately evaluate their ad competition. That‚Äôs why we‚Äôre seeing the emergence of tools like the Facebook Ads library or Google‚Äôs Ad Transparency Center, and now, the TikTok Ads library.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library home screen example" width="618" height="442" class="aligncenter wp-image-75945 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library.jpg 618w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-480x343.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 618px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>The TikTok Ads library is a directory of all ads that have been shown on TikTok. Both users and advertisers alike can use it as a tool to learn about what ads are being published by different businesses, what targeting tactics were applied, and more&#8230;</p>
<p>That ‚Äúmore‚Äù part will be precisely what we‚Äôll discuss today as we walk through all the important TikTok Ads library details you need to know.</p>
<p>Let‚Äôs get started!</p>
<div class='et-box et-shadow'>
					<div class='et-box-content'><h3>Table of contents</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#what">What is the TikTok Ads library?</a></li>
<li><a href="#how">How to use the TikTok Ads library</a></li>
<li><a href="#ways">Ways to create better ads using the TikTok Ads library</a></li>
</ul></div></div>
<div id="what"></div>
<h2>What is the TikTok Ads library?</h2>
<p>The <a href="https://library.tiktok.com/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok Ads library</a> is a one-stop-shop for anyone around the world looking to gather information about an ad that‚Äôs running on TikTok. You don‚Äôt have to be a TikTok user or advertiser to access the TikTok Ads library. Currently, the TikTok Ads library only pulls data from ads running in Europe.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-countries.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - available country data example" width="777" height="427" class="aligncenter wp-image-75944 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-countries.jpg 777w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-countries-480x264.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 777px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Now, that doesn‚Äôt mean the TikTok Ads library can‚Äôt be useful for your business if you‚Äôre located outside of Europe. You can still use this tool to get a general idea of how TikTok Ads in your industry are being approached by businesses like yours (more on this later).</p>
<p>However, if you‚Äôre looking for insight on TikTok ads from businesses located outside the countries outlined in the TikTok Ads library, you can head to the TikTok Creative Center. The ‚ÄúTop Ads Dashboard‚Äù within the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/inspiration/topads/pc/en?period=30" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok Creative Center‚Äôs ‚ÄúInspiration‚Äù tab</a> allows you to search top-performing ads on TikTok from all countries the app is available in. Yet, keep in mind that this will only show you a view of top performers and isn‚Äôt necessarily an online directory of all ads running (regardless of performance) like the TikTok Ads library.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-creative-center.jpg" alt="tiktok ads creative center screenshot" width="794" height="403" class="aligncenter wp-image-75946 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-creative-center.jpg 794w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-creative-center-480x244.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 794px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>If you‚Äôre familiar with the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/06/06/facebook-ad-library" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook ads library</a>, it can be helpful to know that the TikTok Ads library functions in the same way where it‚Äôs meant to provide transparency for users and help businesses source inspiration for ads.</p>
<p>That said, the TikTok Ads library is arguably better than the Facebook Ads library since it provides sorting features to help you find the best (or worst) ads based on multiple filter parameters. Additionally, the TikTok Ads library detail pages are a bit more in-depth than the Facebook Ads library ad detail pages since they incorporate data on the ad‚Äôs targeting and reach.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-targeting-summary.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - targeting summary example" width="765" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-75957 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-targeting-summary.jpg 765w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-targeting-summary-480x376.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 765px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>You can learn more about how <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/02/07/facebook-vs-tiktok-ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok Ads compare to Facebook Ads</a> here.</p>
<div class='et-box et-shadow'>
					<div class='et-box-content'><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="üö®" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Free download &gt;&gt; <a href="https://marketing.wordstream.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsite36CallToActionPhrases.html?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_36CallToActionPhrases_Download">The Best Call to Action Phrases (&amp; Why They Work)</a></div></div>
<h3>More TikTok Ads library features and terms to know</h3>
<p>The standard TikTok Ads library for European data branches out into a few more tabs if you‚Äôre looking for general information on the patterns of TikTok advertising or <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/tiktok-algorithm">organic TikTok content</a>. For example, the ‚ÄúAll ads report‚Äù shows you the total number of ads posted by country and by day, which can be interesting when <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/seasonal-marketing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">planning your seasonal marketing</a>.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-ad-report.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - all ads report example" width="744" height="567" class="aligncenter wp-image-75948 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-ad-report.jpg 744w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-ad-report-480x366.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 744px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>For instance, you‚Äôll find below that more ads were posted during this past year‚Äôs holiday season than during the summer season. This could mean that <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/08/29/holiday-marketing-trends" target="_blank" rel="noopener">holiday marketing</a> on TikTok is fiercely competitive, so you should <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/08/23/tiktok-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plan your TikTok ad content</a> accordingly. (Pro tip: find the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/02/09/best-time-to-post-on-tiktok" target="_blank" rel="noopener">best times to post on TikTok</a> year-round here!)</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-ads-by-day.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - tiktok ads by day chart" width="808" height="446" class="aligncenter wp-image-75947 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-ads-by-day.jpg 808w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-ads-by-day-480x265.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 808px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>For insight on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/10/07/how-to-get-on-tiktok-fyp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">non-paid, organic TikToks</a> you can head over to the ‚ÄúOther commercial content‚Äù tab. This still focuses on content designated as ‚Äúcommercial‚Äù in nature by creators. So, it weeds any TikToks from users that are solely for entertainment purposes and focuses on TikToks meant to <a href="https://marketing.wordstream.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsite30BestWaysToPromote.html?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_Marketing_The30BestWaysToPromoteYourBusiness_Download" target="_blank" rel="noopener">promote a product or service</a>‚Äîwhether it be from a business‚Äôs direct account or an influencer.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-commercial-content-library-1.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - tiktok commercial content library home screen" width="738" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-75960 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-commercial-content-library-1.jpg 738w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-commercial-content-library-1-480x390.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 738px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>The TikTok Creative Center also offers these types of resources for businesses around the world. For example, the TikTok Creative Center is where you can find TikTok‚Äôs other popular library: the <a href="https://ads.tiktok.com/business/creativecenter/music/pc/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Commercial Music Library</a>. You could use the TikTok Commercial Music Library in unison with the TikTok Ads library to find inspiration for video formats in combination with different audio clips.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-commercial-music-library.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - commercial music library screenshot" width="827" height="480" class="aligncenter wp-image-75954 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-commercial-music-library.jpg 827w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-commercial-music-library-480x279.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 827px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Lastly, whether you‚Äôre checking out TikToks within the TikTok Ads library or the Creative Center, there are few core terms you‚Äôll want to be familiar with:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>First shown:</strong> First shown date is the day that the ad received its first impression, regardless of when it was published.</li>
<li><strong>Last shown: </strong>Last shown date is the day when the ad received its last impression, regardless of when it was taken down.</li>
<li><strong>Unique users seen:</strong> The estimated number of unique TikTok users who have seen the ad at least once.</li>
</ul>
<p>Ready to put your foundational knowledge of the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/08/11/advertising-on-tiktok" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok Ads</a> library to work? Let‚Äôs learn the steps to actually <em>use</em> the TikTok Ads library&#8230;</p>
<div id="how"></div>
<h2>How to use the TikTok Ads library</h2>
<p>Here‚Äôs how you can access and use the TikTok Ads library:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Navigate</strong> to <a href="https://library.tiktok.com/ads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://library.tiktok.com/ads/</a>.</li>
<li><strong>Follow the prompts to filter</strong> out for a specific type of TikTok Ad. This is where you can choose to see ads from specific countries, or find ads that fit different formats, publishing dates, <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/keywords?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_Keywords_KWTool">keywords</a>, or even a specific brand name.</li>
<li>Once your filters are set, <strong>click the red search box</strong> on the far right.</li>
<li><strong>Sort your results</strong> using the drop-down menu on the right. This is where you can sort to quickly find the most or least popular ads, as well as the newest and oldest.</li>
<li>If you spot an ad in your results that you want to learn more about, you can <strong>click the play button </strong>to watch the TikTok ad. Alternatively, you can click anywhere on that ad‚Äôs tile to be taken to a separate detail page to find information on the ad‚Äôs target audience size, location, gender, and more.</li>
<li>Congratulations, you‚Äôre now able to use the TikTok Ads library to help your business gain a competitive edge!</li>
</ol>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-detail-page-ad-summary.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - ad detail page example" width="769" height="578" class="aligncenter wp-image-75953 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-detail-page-ad-summary.jpg 769w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-detail-page-ad-summary-480x361.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 769px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>What to do when no ads show in your TikTok Ads library search results</h3>
<p>Did you follow the steps above to use the TikTok Ads library, but nothing came up? That‚Äôs okay! TikTok outlines this as a possibility on the TikTok Ads library home screen:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-no-results.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - zero search results troubleshooting screen from tiktok" width="852" height="437" class="aligncenter wp-image-75952 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-no-results.jpg 852w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-no-results-480x246.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 852px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Basically, you might not always find what you‚Äôre looking for on the TikTok Ads library because of the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>You‚Äôre looking for a specific advertiser that isn‚Äôt currently running ads or doesn‚Äôt run ads within your set country.</li>
<li>No ads match your filter criteria.</li>
<li>You‚Äôre looking for a political or election ad, which is not currently supported by the TikTok Ads library.</li>
<li>The ads you‚Äôre looking for are too fresh. There‚Äôs a slight delay in the TikTok Ads library data where it can occasionally take up to 24 hours to process updates.</li>
</ul>
<p>Luckily, there‚Äôs no usage limits on the TikTok Ads library. Once you troubleshoot your initial search, you can run it again to bring up results. Now, it‚Äôs time to use those results to your advantage!</p>
<div id="ways"></div>
<h2>11 ways to create better content using the TikTok Ads library</h2>
<p>You have all the <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/tiktok-ad-examples/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok ad examples</a> you need at your fingertips thanks to the TikTok Ads library, here‚Äôs how you can take advantage of this unique resource for your business:</p>
<h3>1. Filter to see top performers</h3>
<p>Finding a high-performing TikTok ad from the TikTok Ads library filters alone can feel like you‚Äôre searching for a needle in a haystack. It‚Äôs a good idea to layer one of the sorting options from the drop-down menu on the right. For example, if you sort by ‚ÄúUnique users seen: high to low‚Äù you can find the ads that had the most reach out of all the ones that populated in your search.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-sort-filter.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - example of sorting for best performing ads" width="614" height="608" class="aligncenter wp-image-75951 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-sort-filter.jpg 614w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-sort-filter-480x475.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 614px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>2. Learn which content ideas you<em> don‚Äôt </em>like</h3>
<p>As you poke around in the TikTok Ads library, don‚Äôt only admire ads you‚Äôd like to replicate. Instead, try taking a different approach to see the types of TikTok ads you don‚Äôt like.</p>
<p>Of course, you can get an understanding of this by using the sorting filter to see an older ad or one with a lower number of unique users seen.</p>
<p>However, you can also learn which TikTok ad styles may be better performers but don‚Äôt align with your brand or <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/06/09/company-core-values" target="_blank" rel="noopener">company core values</a>. That way, you can start to understand which types of TikTok Ads to avoid over others when creating and <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-edit-tiktok-videos/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">editing your own TikTok videos</a>.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-sort-features.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - sorting example" width="645" height="502" class="aligncenter wp-image-75950 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-sort-features.jpg 645w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-sort-features-480x374.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 645px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>3. Peek at your competitors&#8217; TikTok ads</h3>
<p>One of the best parts of the TikTok Ads library? You can search for a specific advertiser&#8217;s name! If you want to go after a competitor and you know their name on TikTok, you can plug it into the ‚ÄúAdvertiser name or keyword‚Äù field when setting your search parameters. That way, you can see the ads they‚Äôve posted and compare them against your own strategy.</p>
<p>Another approach would be to search by a core keyword term for your business to evaluate any new competitors on TikTok or to simply see the number and quality of TikTok Ads for that particular product or service offering.</p>
<div class='et-box et-shadow'>
					<div class='et-box-content'><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f50d.png" alt="üîç" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Get ideas for keywords to search for in the TikTok Ads library using our <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/keywords?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_Keywords_KWTool" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Free Keyword Tool</a>!</div></div>
<h3>4. Check out stats and set goals</h3>
<p>Another super stellar feature that the TikTok Ads library provides is basic performance stats for each ad. This can give you a real view of how ads like yours should be performing. Try searching for ads within your industry and take note of the number of unique users seen compared to the target audience size on the detail page.</p>
<p>To track your own TikTok Ads performance, you‚Äôll need <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/05/15/google-ads-benchmarks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">baseline performance benchmarks</a> to measure your progress against. That way, you can set trackable goals based on the average ad performance within your industry. Using this feature within the TikTok Ads library can help you do just that!</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-targeting-summary-overview.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - ad summary report" width="689" height="537" class="aligncenter wp-image-75949 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-targeting-summary-overview.jpg 689w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-targeting-summary-overview-480x374.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 689px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>5. Find popular hashtags</h3>
<p><a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-use-hashtags-with-hashtag-ideas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hashtags</a> can be added to your TikTok ads to help interested users find your content. When you‚Äôre short of <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/04/07/tiktok-hashtags" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok hashtag ideas</a>, the TikTok Ads library can help. When you watch each ad shown in a TikTok Ads library search, you‚Äôre able to get an understanding of which captions or core hashtag terms that business might be using. This can help you find new or trending hashtags to use based on other top-performing ads, or it could even inspire you to create your own spin on a popular hashtag.</p>
<h3>6. Get fresh audio ideas</h3>
<p>Since you can playback TikTok ads right from within the TikTok Ads library search results, you can see which audio clips have brought other advertisers positive (or negative) results. This can help you pre-plan which audio you want to use in your next TikTok Ad clips. Additionally, if there‚Äôs a trending audio clip that you want to use but can‚Äôt think of a video script to go along with it, the TikTok Ads library can help with that, too.</p>
<h3>7. See which trends are coming and going</h3>
<p>There‚Äôs nothing more ‚Äúcringe‚Äù (as TikTokers would say) than creating a video based on a popular trend only to find that trend to be considered ‚Äúold news‚Äù by the time it reaches your audience. TikTok trends are always rapidly changing, so you can use the TikTok Ads library to stay up to date on the latest and greatest of TikTok. Use the sort filter to compare and contrast new and old TikTok Ads. This can help you predict what types of TikTok ads will be more or less popular in the future.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-new-to-old.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - sorting for new trends example" width="582" height="482" class="aligncenter wp-image-75956 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-new-to-old.jpg 582w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-new-to-old-480x398.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 582px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>8. Find the right influencer for your business</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2015/02/26/influencer-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Influencer marketing</a> is a great way to position your brand on TikTok‚Äîespecially if you‚Äôre struggling to establish a presence on the platform by yourself. However, sourcing influencers willing to partner with you can often be a <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/small-business-challenges/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">small business challenge</a>.</p>
<p>Luckily, many TikTok ads already feature influencers that specialize in creating branded content for businesses. In the TikTok Ads library, if you see a business similar to yours that is leveraging an influencer, that influencer (or other influencers in their circle) could be a potential target for you to partner with!</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-tiktok-influencer-ad.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - tiktok influencer ad example" width="264" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-75959 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-tiktok-influencer-ad.jpg 264w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-tiktok-influencer-ad-132x300.jpg 132w" sizes="(max-width: 264px) 100vw, 264px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>An example TikTok Ad created by an influencer rather than the business itself. </em></p>
<h3>9. Source businesses for future partnerships</h3>
<p>Along with influencers to partner with, you can also find businesses to collaborate with through the TikTok Ads library. Try <a href="https://marketing.wordstream.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsiteBigEasyKeyword.html?cid=Web_Any_Homepage_PPC_BigEasyKeyword_Download" target="_blank" rel="noopener">searching for keywords</a> that are complementary to your business and see which businesses are running high-performing ads for that topic.</p>
<p>You could reach out to the business directly or try to <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/03/11/how-to-stitch-on-tiktok" target="_blank" rel="noopener">duet their video</a> to connect with them. From there, you could shout one another out on TikTok or <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/04/01/how-to-go-live-on-tiktok" target="_blank" rel="noopener">go live on TikTok</a> together!</p>
<h3>10. Client prospecting</h3>
<p>Calling all <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2015/07/15/ppc-agency-pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PPC agencies</a>! The TikTok Ads library isn‚Äôt just for assessing your competition or potential promotional partners. Since you can search for <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/tiktok-ads-bidding">TikTok Ads</a> that fit within a certain industry, use this as an opportunity to identify poor-performing ads in your target client‚Äôs verticals. This could be a great way to open the door for prospecting since you could use their TikTok Ad to start a conversation about how your agency could help them improve.</p>
<h3>11. Learn new targeting tactics</h3>
<p>Unlike the Facebook Ads library, the TikTok Ads library ad detail pages provide you with information on any given advertiser‚Äôs targeting tactics. However, keep in mind that TikTok explains that there may be other targeting parameters involved that aren‚Äôt shown on the detail page.</p>
<p>That said, you can get an idea of how other businesses are approaching their TikTok Ad targeting‚Äîwhich can be helpful when you need new ways to show to an ideal audience.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-targeting-details.jpg" alt="tiktok ads library - tiktok ad targeting details" width="681" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-75958 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-targeting-details.jpg 681w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tiktok-ads-library-targeting-details-480x423.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 681px, 100vw" /></p>
<h2>Get ahead with the TikTok Ads library</h2>
<p>The TikTok Ads library, just like the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/google-ads-library">Google Ads library</a>, is an open book chock full of information about what‚Äôs hot for advertisers on the platform. You can use the TikTok Ads library to help your business stand out from the competition and squeeze the most out of your TikTok Ad spend. It can also be a useful tool when you want to discover new audience demographic combinations to target. If you still want more help with your TikTok Ads, see how <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/marketing-services">our solutions</a> can help your business get more customers from TikTok, and maybe even become the next viral sensation!</p>
<p>To recap, here are the top ways you can use the TikTok Ads library:</p>
<ol>
<li>Filter to see top performers</li>
<li>Learn which content ideas you don&#8217;t like</li>
<li>Peek at your competitors&#8217; TikTok ads</li>
<li>Check out stats and set goals</li>
<li>Find popular hashtags</li>
<li>Get fresh audio ideas</li>
<li>See which trends are coming and going</li>
<li>Find the right influencer for your business</li>
<li>Source businesses for future partnerships</li>
<li>Client prospecting</li>
<li>Learn new targeting tactics</li>
</ol>
