<h2>Start targeting the right TikTok audiences with your ads</h2>
<p>TikTok can be a highly effective platform for social media marketers, as long as you‚Äôre equipped with a smart, reactive, and data-driven targeting strategy.</p>
<p>By following all of the best practices in this guide, you‚Äôll be able to unlock the full potential of TikTok advertising and discover hugely profitable audiences.</p>
<p>Here are the best strategies for effective TikTok ads targeting:</p>
<ol>
<li class="p1"><span class="s1">Leverage your existing customer data¬†¬†<span class="Apple-converted-space">¬†</span></span></li>
<li class="p1"><span class="s1">Utilize interest and behavior targeting <span class="Apple-converted-space">¬†</span></span></li>
<li class="p1"><span class="s1">Harness the power of Custom Audiences<span class="Apple-converted-space">¬†</span></span></li>
<li class="p1"><span class="s1">Capitalize on Lookalike segments¬†<span class="Apple-converted-space">¬†</span></span></li>
<li class="p1"><span class="s1">Analyze performance data and then optimize¬†¬†<span class="Apple-converted-space">¬†</span></span></li>
<li class="p1"><span class="s1">Use A/B testing to fuel superior targeting</span></li>
</ol>
<p>Tick all of these boxes, and you‚Äôll be driving conversions from high-value audiences before you know it.</p>
